<h4>Use As</h4>
<p>
    <xmp>
        TABLE:
        Client0: k0 generate bảng này xuống client
        Index0: bảng chính
        Index1: bảng phụ cấp 1
        menu: tạo menu cho bảng này
        report: bảng report
        notification: bảng notfiy
        COLUMN:
        diplaynone: generate display:none control
        hidden: generate hidden control
        parent: field is parent id or parent key
        owner: field is owned user id
        scope: field is using as scope of app
        optionvalue: field is value of option in select control
        optiontext: field is text of option in select control
        title: field is title of record
        number: field is number type, generate number input control
        tel: field is tel type, generate tel input control
        email: field is email type, generate email input control
        date: field is date type, generate date control
        select: field is select type, mapped to other table, generate select control
        editor: field is long text type, generate textarea control
    </xmp>
</p>